Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我这人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌的就是有能力做去不去做的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算上兰华
